</li>\n</ul>\n<pre><code>域名是注册局开放的，通过平台注册的，域名是及时产品的，正常是无法退款的.\n</code></pre>\n<ul>\n<li>如果域名有敏感词，那么为什么还能在阿里云上购买注册成功呢？</li>\n</ul>\n","last_modified":1664412817,"replies":15,"id":883703},{"node":{"avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6c34/0f25/1063_large.png?m=1645243654","name":"cpp","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6c34/0f25/1063_normal.png?m=1645243654","title":"C++","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/cpp","topics":389,"footer":"","header":"关于编程语言 C++ 的使用讨论","title_alternative":"C++","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6c34/0f25/1063_mini.png?m=1645243654","stars":571,"aliases":[],"root":false,"id":1063,"parent_node_name":"programming"},"member":{"id":528693,"username":"Ross249","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/Ross249","website":"jimmieluo.com","twitter":"JimLuo_","psn":"Luois_Ross","github":"","btc":"","location":"","tagline":"","bio":"","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/d76b/d112/528693_mini.png?m=1662644883","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/d76b/d112/528693_normal.png?m=1662644883","avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/d76b/d112/528693_large.png?m=1662644883","avatar_xlarge":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/d76b/d112/528693_xlarge.png?m=1662644883","avatar_xxlarge":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/d76b/d112/528693_xlarge.png?m=1662644883","avatar_xxxlarge":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/d76b/d112/528693_xlarge.png?m=1662644883","created":1610854781,"last_modified":1662644883},"last_reply_by":"star9029","last_touched":1664419417,"title":"寻几个 C++练手的项目","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/883697","created":1664410729,"deleted":0,"content":"## 背景：\r\n最近学了一圈 C++、OpenGL 和图形学相关的知识，想找些简单易上手的项目练练手\r\n\r\n## 选项：\r\n- 与图形学相关\r\n- 与游戏相关亦可\r\n\r\n## 此外：\r\n如果有其他领域的优秀项目也欢迎各位老哥留下项目名称或地址","content_rendered":"<h2>背景：</h2>\n<p>最近学了一圈 C++、OpenGL 和图形学相关的知识，想找些简单易上手的项目练练手</p>\n<h2>选项：</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>与图形学相关</li>\n<li>与游戏相关亦可</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>此外：</h2>\n<p>如果有其他领域的优秀项目也欢迎各位老哥留下项目名称或地址</p>\n","last_modified":1664410729,"replies":11,"id":883697},{"node"